        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>metal decorating techniques [300054012], metalworking processes and techniques [300053947], metalworking and metalworking processes and techniques [300155055], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
